{"tid":1126321,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇見過傻仔玩機動遊戲時跌左部電話落街？","createTime":"2019-04-26T10:07:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T08:50:47.000Z","uid":180371,"like":1681,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":133,"replies":[{"pid":"d359f57b264ee7965bba11f3d896135e8fcbb9c2","tid":1126321,"uid":180371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:07:15.000Z","msg":"嗰個傻仔就係我<br />\n話說前幾日女友生日同佢去海洋公園，貪有張生日飛，仲事前特登去買左張early bird 飛<br />\n咁一開始都好地地，直到去玩完小丑過山車之後，行左唔夠一分鐘，諗住拎部電話出黎㩒下<br />\n搵極都搵唔到，再諗返先醒起去玩前唔記得放部電話入去個袋入面<br />\n即係袋住黎玩，玩玩下跌左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即刻去同職員講：唔好意思我啱先玩小丑過山車時唔記得放低個電話好似跌左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nfeel到個職員忍笑忍得好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n過左兩日，個職員打電話黎，話已經搵返我部電話啦，叫我返去攞<br />\n我就即刻狗衝過去拎返<br />\n<br />\n我心存一絲希望後拎返部電話係咁嘅樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tMeNYXc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtMeNYXc.jpg&h=bafcb916&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jBtGiXd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjBtGiXd.jpg&h=be6311f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0hHsevz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0hHsevz.jpg&h=72d0f490&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住拎左去apple問有冇得整<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZCzDXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZCzDXL.jpg&h=43184c5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後比左$2800換左部翻新機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yAcLLC3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyAcLLC3.jpg&h=9ad90951&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0fb94d05ffc6d5f8760408ba3930571235b65b8","tid":1126321,"uid":30678,"like":581,"dislike":2,"score":579,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:08:45.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"39ed23297e000fdb47f9d199c8b9d4a13c981870","tid":1126321,"uid":168730,"like":189,"dislike":3,"score":186,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:08:51.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"7deda6c5fa73fd42efde52a448bed77aae7689c3","tid":1126321,"uid":62850,"like":145,"dislike":1,"score":144,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:09:50.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"460da1f76cc1e55292769a95a89187d2ec351d2f","tid":1126321,"uid":158411,"like":128,"dislike":2,"score":126,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:09:53.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"8b679c28269fb821c4f4d8745f759e0752e4b942","tid":1126321,"uid":136074,"like":315,"dislike":9,"score":306,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:09:54.000Z","msg":"傻撚閪"},{"pid":"e6a99dd016b523c7a71f9f94df47104df211f20c","tid":1126321,"uid":48174,"like":530,"dislike":16,"score":514,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:09:54.000Z","msg":"試過玩4D影院跌左部電話入椅入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b19c11aeb418f1ade30797eecc92b2afe139882e","tid":1126321,"uid":50041,"like":778,"dislike":6,"score":772,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:10:12.000Z","msg":"如果部電話飛左出去傷到人就奶野"},{"pid":"896851c32309655e23822d824b1db5f93f12522f","tid":1126321,"uid":201604,"like":50,"dislike":3,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:10:15.000Z","msg":"第一個係你 你好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b91b3c3ca99cae5ddd3b18adbb7d9fe02abdbd7","tid":1126321,"uid":198932,"like":200,"dislike":4,"score":196,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:10:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/26/181034_2251c6ca89fb50f9350d133b49fb5f36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F26%2F181034_2251c6ca89fb50f9350d133b49fb5f36.jpg&h=6b9668bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f28a68b3f84e1436261a3a67934a12486f8ad97f","tid":1126321,"uid":9193,"like":105,"dislike":2,"score":103