/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跌咗落路軌，好彩冇跌出去扔到其他人。<br />\n之後填左form，要勞煩維修人員夜晚檢查嘅時候幫我搵。<br />\n最後第二日通知我已經搵返，真心好多謝海洋公園啲工作人員。<br />\n從此去主題樂園玩機動遊戲都好小心。<br />\n<br />\n如果有工作人員見到呢個post，你地平時應該幫人執唔少失物，唔好意思，唔該哂。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82d69eab72c5038e4634e624e2ab7b2920d22ea8","tid":1126321,"uid":17574,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T17:54:26.000Z","msg":"我都有試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該都有差唔多兩年半<br />\n嗰次去op續張annual pass 順便入去玩少少野先走<br />\n又係玩呢個小丑 <br />\n玩完都唔覺既 臨走嗰下先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰晚打返自己電話知道啲員工執到<br />\n第二日再返入去攞返<br />\n神奇地部電話冇穿冇爛 淨係其中一個角位突起咗少少<br />\n嗰陣除咗覺得自己好好彩之外 仲覺得部機真係超襟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申: 當時部iPhone SE買咗2個月 到而家都仲用做副機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSE好波 希望有生之年可以見到SE2啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53b39f3217e1e1932069f48b51e86a88d419165b","tid":1126321,"uid":241810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T18:01:04.000Z","msg":"You may consider a nice protective case <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"defa3c951edac837fd23054e566346a531b0a51c","tid":1126321,"uid":30673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"589b2bc270617ad2094ed65649548766bf126585","tid":1126321,"uid":132030,"like":145,"dislike":1,"score":144,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:33:54.000Z","msg":"我試過玩碰碰車 撞到電話跌咗落地<br />\n之後我叫住唔好 但個細路大笑一野展過我部電話<br />\n爆撚曬 <br />\n個細路將來一定有報應"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T18:02:20.000Z","msg":"有冇下文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌哂鬼咁就算?"},{"pid":"80e3ed8b81448b94216bbde7ebaf3fb1e990eb0a","tid":1126321,"uid":65400,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T18:20:13.000Z","msg":"跌完嘢重覺得好撚過癮 好撚彩冇傷